text: Jana Čepelová was the defending champion, having won the event in 2013, however she lost in the first round to Alexandra Panova. Alexandra Dulgheru won the title, defeating Kimiko Date-Krumm in the final, 6–3, 6–4. == Seeds == == Main draw == === Finals === === Top half === === Bottom half === == References == * Main draw Al Habtoor Tennis Challenge - Singles Category:Al Habtoor Tennis Challenge Category:2014 in Emirati sport
